://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/living-world/2023/saving-endangered-flightless-birds-of-new-zealand</guid></item><item><title>尼安德特人：现在比以往任何时候都更加了解</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/society/2023/new-finds-about-neanderthal-brains-and-behavior</link><description>自从我们第一次发现他们的遗骸以来，他们就一直让我们着迷。如今，得益于新的文物和技术，有关我们近亲的发现正在大量而迅速地涌现。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 18:13:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/society/2023/new-finds-about-neanderthal-brains-and-behavior</guid></item><item><title>绿色航运提速</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/technology/2023/how-to-turn-the-shipping-industry-green</link><description>一项国际条约旨在到 2050 年左右使航运业实现净零排放。新型燃料、风能和全球范围内的协调能否实现这一目标？</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 18:13:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/technology/2023/how-to-turn-the-shipping-industry-green</guid></item><item><title>冰架解剖和空间激光器</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/newsletter/2023/2023-11-19</link><description>另外，塑料将生物从海岸带到开放水域</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 18:13:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/newsletter/2023/2023-11-19</guid></item><item><title>了解极地冰盖的竞赛</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/food-environment/2023/race-to-understand-polar-ice-sheets</link><description>随着冰川悬崖断裂并破坏冰冻景观的稳定性，冰川学家理查德·艾利将注意力集中在裂缝上。这项工作可以改善对未来海平面上升的预测。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 18:13:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/food-environment/2023/race-to-understand-polar-ice-sheets</guid></item><item><title>在太平洋垃圾带，新的海洋生态系统正在蓬勃发展</title><link>https://knowablemagazine.org/content/article/food-environment/2023/in-great-pacific-garbage-patch-new-marine-ecosystems</link><description>粘在塑料瓶和其他人类垃圾上的海洋生物已经远离沿海栖息地，可能会威胁到当地物种</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 18:13:41 GMT</pubDate><gui